name: There Used To Be A Beautiful Lake... Process
description: There Used To Be A Beautiful Lake... Process My first ever process video as NFT & first ever HEN drop. I believe the process visuals can be just as beautiful as a finished piece. It documents the journey of its creator. You get to watch me play, think and make mistakes and then reverse them. Like a memory of making which you may have never seen. This is what lies behind my latest 1/1: There Used To Be A Beautiful Lake...
